#### Steps & Code to Reproduce

Other Libraries using Annotation Processing Like Dagger2 do work using `annotationProcessor` 
#### Code Sample

 groovy
buildscript {
    repositories {
        jcenter()
    }
    dependencies {
        classpath 'com.android.tools.build:gradle:2.2.0-alpha3'
